# LfrCache registry. Copy to enabled-repos.txt (gitignored), or just run
# `lfrCache on <repo>` which manages it for you. One absolute repo or worktree
# root path per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Example:
# /home/me/liferay/repos/liferay-portal
# /home/me/liferay/repos/liferay-portal-7.4.x
